snippet.title: Hibernaculum Teaser
snippet.description:
Hibernaculum is a survival horror RPG/ dungeon crawler. 

For more information perhaps consider joining our Patreon which both helps support and speed up development, plus you'll get some insights into the game's progress & behind the scenes extras;

https://www.patreon.com/wormwoodstudios

Or follow me on Twitter, or stay tuned for more updates here!

https://twitter.com/modredcastleton
